snippet.title: Paths & Danger Teaser Trailer ⚔️
snippet.description:
It's here! Our newest game that took two years in the making has finally arrived! As we are just two developers, we just launched a Kickstarter campaign to get the opportunity to add more content to the game! 
Please take a look and consider supporting it! 

⚔️ Paths & Danger on Steam👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1403990/Paths__Danger/

Be part of this journey, be part of #PathsandDanger !!

https://goldengodgames.com/pathsanddanger/



***

Follow the latest game updates on Social Media

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/goldengodgames

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/goldengod.games/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/GoldenGodGames
